e.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/opentelemetry-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/opentelemetry-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "OpenTelemetry \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "OpenTelemetry\uc758 \uc2e0\ud638 3\uc885, API\u00b7SDK\u00b7Collector\u00b7OTLP \uad6c\uc131, \uc218\ub3d9\u00b7\uc790\ub3d9 \uacc4\uce21\uacfc head\u00b7tail \uc0d8\ud50c\ub9c1, Collector \ubc30\ud3ec \ud328\ud134\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/opentelemetry-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:59:23+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-20T23:22:40+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["SRE"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/21/s3-%EC%84%B1%EB%8A%A5%EB%B9%84%EC%9A%A9-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/21/s3-%EC%84%B1%EB%8A%A5%EB%B9%84%EC%9A%A9-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "S3 \uc131\ub2a5\u00b7\ube44\uc6a9 \ucd5c\uc801\ud654 \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "S3 \uc2a4\ud1a0\ub9ac\uc9c0 \ud074\ub798\uc2a4\ubcc4 \ucd5c\uc18c \ubcf4\uad00\u00b7\uac80\uc0c9 \ube44\uc6a9, \ub77c\uc774\ud504\uc0ac\uc774\ud074 \uc804\ud658 \ud568\uc815, \ud504\ub9ac\ud53d\uc2a4 \uc694\uccad \ud55c\ub3c4\uc640 \uba40\ud2f0\ud30c\ud2b8\u00b7Express One Zone\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc131\ub2a5\u00b7\ube44\uc6a9 \ucd5c\uc801\ud654 \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/21/s3-\uc131\ub2a5\ube44\uc6a9-\ucd5c\uc801\ud654-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:59:23+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-21T21:46:22+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/21/systemd-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/21/systemd-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "systemd \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "systemd\uc758 \uc720\ub2db \uc885\ub958\uc640 \uc11c\ube44\uc2a4 Type, \uc758\uc874\uc131, Restart \uc815\ucc45, cgroup \ub9ac\uc18c\uc2a4 \uc81c\uc5b4, \ud0c0\uc774\uba38, target \ubd80\ud305, journald \uad6c\uc870\ub97c \ud45c\ub85c \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/21/systemd-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:59:23+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-21T21:46:22+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Linux"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/19/edge-association-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B0%98-utm-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/19/edge-association-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B0%98-utm-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "Edge Association \uae30\ubc18 UTM \uad6c\uc131 \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "AWS Edge Association\uc73c\ub85c \uc778\ubc14\uc6b4\ub4dc \ud2b8\ub798\ud53d\uc744 UTM\uc5d0 \uc6b0\ud68c\uc2dc\ud0a4\ub294 \uad6c\uc131\uacfc ENI \uc9c1\uc811 \uc9c0\uc815\u00b7GWLB(GENEVE) \ubc29\uc2dd \ube44\uad50 \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/19/edge-association-\uae30\ubc18-utm-\uad6c\uc131-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:59:23+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-19T10:15:02+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/wireguard-vs-ipip-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/wireguard-vs-ipip-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "WireGuard vs IPIP \ucc28\uc774\uc810 \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "IPIP\uc640 WireGuard\uc758 \ucea1\uc290\ud654\u00b7\uc554\ud638\ud654 \uc6d0\ub9ac\uc640 Noise_IK \ud578\ub4dc\uc170\uc774\ud06c\u00b7cryptokey routing \ucc28\uc774\ub97c \ube44\uad50\ud45c\ub85c \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/wireguard-vs-ipip-\ucc28\uc774\uc810-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:59:23+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-20T23:22:40+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Network"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/gitops%EC%99%80-argocd-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/gitops%EC%99%80-argocd-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "GitOps\uc640 ArgoCD \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "GitOps \ub124 \uc6d0\uce59\uacfc ArgoCD \uc544\ud0a4\ud14d\ucc98, push\u00b7pull \ubaa8\ub378 \ucc28\uc774, \ub3d9\uae30\ud654 \uc815\ucc45, Flux\uc640\uc758 \ube44\uad50\uae4c\uc9c0 \ud45c\ub85c \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/gitops\uc640-argocd-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:59:23+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-20T23:22:40+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["DevOps"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EB%82%B4%EB%B6%80-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EB%82%B4%EB%B6%80-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "\ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108 \ub0b4\ubd80 \uad6c\uc870 \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "namespace\u00b7cgroup\ubd80\ud130 dockerd\u00b7containerd\u00b7runc \uacc4\uce35\uacfc dockershim \uc81c\uac70, overlayfs, gVisor\u00b7Kata \ub7f0\ud0c0\uc784 \uc120\ud0dd\uc9c0\uae4c\uc9c0 \ud45c\ub85c \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/\ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108-\ub0b4\ubd80-\uad6c\uc870-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:59:23+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-20T23:22:40+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Docker"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/3-tier-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%9D%B8%ED%94%84%EB%9D%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/3-tier-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%9D%B8%ED%94%84%EB%9D%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1/", "title": "3-Tier \uae30\ubcf8 \uc778\ud504\ub77c \uad6c\uc131", "content_html": "VPC\u00b7\uc11c\ube0c\ub137\u00b7Bastion\u00b7ELB \uc624\ud1a0\uc2a4\ucf00\uc77c\ub9c1\u00b7RDS MySQL\uae4c\uc9c0 AWS 3-Tier \uc778\ud504\ub77c\ub97c \ucf58\uc194\uc5d0\uc11c \uc9c1\uc811 \uad6c\ucd95\ud55c \uc2e4\uc2b5 \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/3-tier-\uae30\ubcf8-\uc778\ud504\ub77c-\uad6c\uc131.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/api-gateway-with-lambda/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/api-gateway-with-lambda/", "title": "API Gateway with Lambda", "content_html": "REST API Gateway\uc5d0 Lambda \ub450 \uac1c\ub97c root\u00b7resource \uacbd\ub85c\ub85c \uc5f0\uacb0\ud558\uace0 GET \ud30c\ub77c\ubbf8\ud130 \ub9e4\ud551\uacfc curl \ud638\ucd9c\uae4c\uc9c0 \ud655\uc778\ud55c \uc2e4\uc2b5", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/api-gateway-with-lambda.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda/", "title": "Access S3, DynamoDB with Lambda", "content_html": "S3 \uac1d\uccb4 \uc0dd\uc131 \uc774\ubca4\ud2b8\ub85c Lambda\ub97c \ud2b8\ub9ac\uac70\ud574 \ud30c\uc77c\uc744 \ucc98\ub9ac\ud558\uace0 DynamoDB\uc5d0 \uc801\uc7ac, test event\ub85c \ubc18\ubcf5 \uac80\uc99d\ud55c \uc2e4\uc2b5", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/failover-for-ha/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/failover-for-ha/", "title": "Failover for HA", "content_html": "Orchestrator GUI\ub85c MySQL \ub9c8\uc2a4\ud130 \uc7a5\uc560 \uc2dc \uc790\ub3d9 \ud398\uc77c\uc624\ubc84\ub97c Docker \ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub85c \uad6c\uc131\ud558\uace0 \uc778\uc704\uc801 \ub2e4\uc6b4\uc73c\ub85c \uc2b9\uaca9\u00b7\ubcf5\uad6c\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc2e4\uc2b5\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/failover-for-ha.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Database"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/s3-object-encryption/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/s3-object-encryption/", "title": "S3 object encryption", "content_html": "S3\uc758 SSE-S3\u00b7SSE-C\u00b7SSE-KMS\u00b7DSSE-KMS \ub124 \ubc29\uc2dd \ucc28\uc774\uc640 \uc5c5\ub85c\ub4dc CLI \uc635\uc158, SSE-KMS boto3 up/download \ucf54\ub4dc\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/s3-object-encryption.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role/", "title": "VPC Endpoint with Role", "content_html": "Bastion Host\ub85c \ud504\ub77c\uc774\ube57 \uc6f9 \uc11c\ubc84\uc5d0 \uc811\uc18d\ud558\uace0 Gateway Endpoint\uc640 IAM Role\ub85c S3\u00b7DynamoDB\uc5d0 \uac8c\uc774\ud2b8\uc6e8\uc774 \uc5c6\uc774 \uc811\uadfc\ud558\ub294 \uc2e4\uc2b5", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/cicd-on-single-container/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/cicd-on-single-container/", "title": "CICD on Single container", "content_html": "React \ub2e8\uc77c \ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub97c Docker\u00b7docker-compose\ub85c \uac1c\ubc1c\u00b7\uc6b4\uc601 \ud658\uacbd \ub098\ub204\uace0, Travis CI\ub85c GitHub\uc5d0\uc11c AWS Beanstalk\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc790\ub3d9 \ubc30\ud3ec\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/cicd-on-single-container.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["DevOps"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/circle-ci-basics/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/circle-ci-basics/", "title": "Circle-CI Basics", "content_html": "CircleCI orbs\ub85c \ud504\ub860\ud2b8\ub294 AWS S3\uc5d0, \ubc31\uc5d4\ub4dc\ub294 CodeDeploy\ub85c EC2\uc5d0 \uc62c\ub9ac\ub294 \ubc30\ud3ec \ud30c\uc774\ud504\ub77c\uc778\uc744 IAM \uad8c\ud55c\ubd80\ud130 \uc124\uc815\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/circle-ci-basics.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["DevOps"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/multi-container-cicd/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/multi-container-cicd/", "title": "Multi container CICD", "content_html": "React\u00b7Node\u00b7Nginx\u00b7MySQL \uba40\ud2f0\ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub97c docker-compose\ub85c \ubb36\uace0 Nginx \ub77c\uc6b0\ud305\uacfc Travis CI\ub85c AWS Beanstalk ECS\uae4c\uc9c0 \ubc30\ud3ec\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/multi-container-cicd.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["DevOps"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-proxy-layer-for-mysql/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-proxy-layer-for-mysql/", "title": "Docker Proxy Layer for MySQL", "content_html": "ProxySQL\ub85c \uc77d\uae30\u00b7\uc4f0\uae30 \ud638\uc2a4\ud2b8\uadf8\ub8f9\uc744 \ub098\ub220 \ucffc\ub9ac\ub97c \ub77c\uc6b0\ud305\ud558\uace0, Master \uc7a5\uc560 \ud6c4 14\ucd08 \ub9cc\uc5d0 \uc2b9\uaca9\ub418\ub294 \ud398\uc77c\uc624\ubc84\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc2e4\uce21\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/docker-proxy-layer-for-mysql.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Database"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-basics/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-basics/", "title": "Docker basics", "content_html": "Node \uc571\uc73c\ub85c Dockerfile\u00b7WORKDIR\u00b7\ub808\uc774\uc5b4 \uce90\uc2f1(\ube4c\ub4dc 6.7\ucd08\uc5d0\uc11c 1.8\ucd08)\u00b7\ubcfc\ub968\u00b7compose\uae4c\uc9c0 \ud6d1\uc740 \ub3c4\ucee4 \ubcf5\uc2b5 \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/docker-basics.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Docker"]}]}